  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether delaying the superficial inferior
      epigastric artery (SIEA) flap results in widening of diameter and enhancing of blood flow of
      its donor artery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
